Asynchronous JavaScript And HTML
AJAX is neither a language, a framework nor a library. It is a set of web technologies to send and receive data from client to a server asynchronously. 

Client---- JS Call ----- AJAX Engine -------- XmlHttpRequest ---------- Server

Server ---- XML/JSON ----- AJAX Engine ---------- HTML Response ------------ Client

XHR is an API in form of an object. 
XML stands for eXtensible Markup Language.


2008 = 6
2011 = 9
(3 years)
